WEBVTT

00:01.060 --> 00:02.618
PREVIOUSLY
ON "VERONICA MARS"...

00:02.670 --> 00:04.558
THEY'RE ALL DEAD.

00:04.600 --> 00:06.431
WOODY'S A PERVERT.
HE'S SICK.

00:06.470 --> 00:07.994
WHAT HE DID TO US
IS WRONG.

00:08.040 --> 00:09.701
TWO OF THE BOYS
WHO DIED IN THE BUS CRASH

00:09.740 --> 00:11.662
WERE ON WOODY'S
LITTLE-LEAGUE TEAM.

00:11.710 --> 00:13.837
MOST ADULTS KEEP THEIR HANDS
OFF OF OTHER PEOPLE'S CHILDREN.

00:13.880 --> 00:15.233
YOU'LL BE THE GUY

00:15.280 --> 00:18.044
WHO LET A CHILD MOLESTER
AND A MURDERER GET AWAY!

00:18.080 --> 00:20.742
WOODY'S GONE.
HE TOOK HIS PRIVATE PLANE.

00:20.780 --> 00:22.987
MY GRANDMOTHER ASKED ME
FOR ONE THING MY WHOLE LIFE.

00:23.020 --> 00:25.648
SHE WANTS TO SEE ME WALK ACROSS
THAT STAGE AT GRADUATION.

00:25.690 --> 00:27.681
Thumper: IT'S WEEVIL!
I'M TELLING YOU!

00:27.720 --> 00:28.687
HE SET ME UP!

00:28.720 --> 00:30.756
I GOT SOMETHING ON YOU.

00:30.790 --> 00:32.849
BLESS ME, FATHER,
FOR I HAVE SINNED.

00:32.900 --> 00:34.253
I'VE GOT WHAT?
CH LAMYDIA.

00:34.300 --> 00:36.188
JACKIE LEFI' FOR FRANCE
THIS MORNING.

00:36.230 --> 00:37.925
I THOUGHT OUR STORY
WAS EPIC.

00:37.970 --> 00:39.164
I HAVE TO GO.

00:39.200 --> 00:40.337
I DON'T WANT TO LOSE YOU
FROM MY LIFE.

00:40.370 --> 00:42.099
MY STEPMOM --
SHE'S A GOLD DIGGER.

00:42.140 --> 00:43.960
YOU'RE CASH-STRAPPED.
I CAN HELP.

00:44.010 --> 00:46.638
BUT QUID PRO QUO,
MRS. C.,

00:46.680 --> 00:48.272
QUID PRO QUO.

00:48.310 --> 00:51.677
Woman: WE FIND THE DEFENDANT
NOT GUILTY.

00:51.710 --> 00:54.372
[ CHEERING ]

00:54.420 --> 00:56.217
Veronica:
SEE, THIS IS HOW IT IS.

00:56.250 --> 00:58.514
THE INNOCENT SUFFER,
THE GUILTY GO FREE,

00:58.550 --> 01:01.917
AND TRUTH AND FICTION ARE
PRE'ITY MUCH INTERCHANGEABLE.

01:01.960 --> 01:04.986
MR. ECHOLLS, HOW DO YOU FEEL
ABOUT YOUR ACQUITTAL?

01:05.030 --> 01:06.793
I FEEL...RELIEVED

01:06.830 --> 01:11.961
TO HAVE MY NAME CLEARED
OF THIS...HORRIBLE CRIME.

01:12.000 --> 01:14.594
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

01:14.640 --> 01:17.700
THERE IS NEITHER A SANTA CLAUS
NOR AN EASTER BUNNY,

01:17.740 --> 01:20.436
AND THERE ARE NO ANGELS
WATCHING OVER US.

01:20.480 --> 01:23.244
THINGS JUST HAPPEN
FOR NO REASON.

01:24.750 --> 01:27.139
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

01:27.180 --> 01:29.148
AND NOTHING MAKES ANY SENSE.

01:29.190 --> 01:30.714
WE WILL NOT DO THIS.

01:30.750 --> 01:32.752
YOU CAN'T LET THIS
STICK IN YOUR HEAD.

01:32.790 --> 01:34.781
HOWEVER WRONG IT TURNED OUT,
IT'S DONE.

01:34.820 --> 01:37.527
WE'RE PEOPLE WITH LIVES,
AND WE WILL NOT OBSESS.

01:37.560 --> 01:38.879
WE MOVE ON.

01:38.930 --> 01:41.922
AARON ECHOLLS WILL GET
HIS JUSTICE IN HIS OWN WAY.

01:41.960 --> 01:43.461
YOU REALLY BELIEVE THAT?

01:43.500 --> 01:47.163
YES. NOW, COME ON.
WE'RE RUNNING A BUSINESS HERE.

01:47.200 --> 01:48.792
LOOK ALIVE.

01:52.440 --> 01:54.237
[ FAX MACHINE WHIRS ]

02:07.220 --> 02:09.723
WHAT HAPPENED
TO MOVING ON?

02:11.030 --> 02:13.055
POSTED TODAY.

02:13.100 --> 02:14.351
MEG'S DAD OFFERING 20 GRAND

02:16.170 --> 02:18.468
WELL, I'M SURE
SOMEONE WILL GET HIM.

02:18.500 --> 02:19.694
DIDN'T YOU SAY SOMETHING

02:19.740 --> 02:21.389
ABOUT "WE HAVE A BUSINESS
TO RUN"?

02:21.440 --> 02:22.737
SHOULDN'T YOU BE OUT

02:22.770 --> 02:24.601
HUNTING HIM DOWN
LIKE THE DOG HE IS?

02:24.640 --> 02:26.972
I ALSO SAID SOMETHING ABOUT
US BEING PEOPLE WITH LIVES.

02:27.010 --> 02:30.207
SEE, I HAVE THIS KID WHO'S GONNA
GRADUATE FROM HIGH SCHOOL.

02:30.250 --> 02:31.274
I DON'T WANT TO MISS IT.

02:31.310 --> 02:32.675
THIS IS WOODY GOODMAN.

02:32.720 --> 02:35.575
HE BLEW UP A BUS
AND MOLESTED CHILDREN.

02:35.620 --> 02:37.485
GUESS I'M JUST
SENTIMENTAL.

02:37.520 --> 02:40.910
WHEN THE MANAGEMENT
GIVES YOU FREE CAKE,

02:40.960 --> 02:43.019
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO EAT IT.

02:44.060 --> 02:46.255
I THOUGHT YOU WERE PREPARED
FOR JACKIE GOING.

02:46.300 --> 02:49.098
NEVER FIGURED IT WOULD
GO DOWN LIKE THIS.

02:49.130 --> 02:51.360
SHE LEFI' YOU A NOTE?

02:51.400 --> 02:52.833
"BUT I WAS AFRAID
IF I SAW YOU,

02:52.870 --> 02:55.236
"I WOULDN'T BE ABLE
TO GET ON THE PLANE.

02:55.270 --> 02:56.737
I'LL ALWAYS..."

02:56.770 --> 03:01.070
WELL, THEN IT'S JUST A BUNCH
OF PRIVATE STUFF.

03:01.110 --> 03:03.249
WHAT CAN YOU DO
ABOUT THAT?

03:03.280 --> 03:04.542
YOU COULD USE A METHOD

03:04.580 --> 03:07.174
TIME-TESTED BY WOMEN
THROUGHOUT THE AGES --

03:07.220 --> 03:09.313
GORGE ON CAKE.

03:09.350 --> 03:11.944
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

03:14.190 --> 03:16.920
JOHNNY LUDDEN.
THANKS FOR DROPPING BY.

03:16.960 --> 03:19.793
SURE. FREE GELATO JUST
TO SHOW UP -- WHY NOT?

03:19.830 --> 03:23.459
IS THIS YOU
ON WOODY'S OLD TEAM?

03:23.500 --> 03:24.467
YEAH.

03:24.500 --> 03:25.819
SO, DO I HAVE TO EAT HERE,

03:25.870 --> 03:27.428
OR CAN I GET THE GELATO
IN THE CARTON?

03:27.470 --> 03:30.462
JUST A FEW MORE
QUESTIONS FIRST.

03:32.280 --> 03:33.304
HEY, HONEY.

03:33.340 --> 03:35.171
HEY, DAD.

03:35.210 --> 03:37.599
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

03:37.650 --> 03:39.709
HELLO?

03:43.190 --> 03:45.442
YOU'VE GOT A CALL...

03:45.490 --> 03:47.651
FROM VINNIE VAN LOWE.

03:47.690 --> 03:49.112
Vinnie: SO...

03:49.160 --> 03:51.378
OF COURSE YOU KNOW ABOUT
THE BOUNTY ON THIS GOODMAN GUY.

03:51.430 --> 03:53.421
I'M AWARE OF IT, YES.

03:53.460 --> 03:55.894
20 G's?
THAT'S BIG-BOY MONEY.

03:55.930 --> 03:58.569
GONNA BE A LOT OF TOP GUYS
OUT THERE FOR IT.

03:58.600 --> 04:01.831
I HAD A THOUGHT.
WE TEAM UP.

04:01.870 --> 04:04.862
MARS AND VAN LOWE.
POOL OUR RESOURCES.

04:04.910 --> 04:06.332
SPLIT THE CASH.

04:06.380 --> 04:09.235
SHERIFF GOT YOU ON VIDEO
BREAKING INTO WOODY'S HOUSE.

04:14.520 --> 04:17.512
BUT JOHNNY LAW
DON'T KNOW WHAT I GOT.

04:17.550 --> 04:18.983
WHAT DO YOU GOT?

04:19.020 --> 04:21.853
ALL HIS RECORDS --
TAX, MEDICAL, CORPORATE --

04:21.890 --> 04:23.050
THE WHOLE ENCHILADA.

04:23.090 --> 04:25.285
WE NAIL HIM,
WE SPLIT 60-40.

04:25.330 --> 04:26.820
I'M THE 60, BY THE WAY.

04:26.860 --> 04:27.827
50-50...

04:27.860 --> 04:29.623
IF THE STUFF YOU GOT
PANS OUT,

04:29.670 --> 04:32.468
AND NO ACTION UNTIL AFTER
MY DAUGHTER'S GRADUATION.

04:32.500 --> 04:35.936
I'M IN JAIL.
I DESERVE 60.

04:36.970 --> 04:39.632
I RISK MY LIFE TO BRING
A FUGITIVE TO JUSTICE,

04:39.680 --> 04:42.308
AND YOU'RE GIVING ME
WORLD'S TINIEST VIOLIN.

04:42.350 --> 04:44.079
GUESS I'M JUST HEARTLESS.

04:44.110 --> 04:46.749
HE'S GOT, LIKE, 10 CREDIT CARDS
IN DIFFERENT CORPORATE NAMES.

04:46.780 --> 04:49.487
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO PUT A TRACE
ON ALL OF THEM.

04:49.520 --> 04:51.841
AND HE HAS A PILOT'S LICENSE.

04:51.890 --> 04:55.951
SEASONAL ALLERGIES,
BAD ARCH ES.

04:55.990 --> 04:57.855
AND HE HAD THE CLAP.

04:57.890 --> 04:59.949
TREATED TWICE
FOR CH LAMYDIA.

05:00.000 --> 05:03.527
DIDN'T SEE THAT
IN HIS CAMPAIGN MATERIALS.

05:06.000 --> 05:09.504
BINGO. HEART ARRHYTHMIA.

05:09.540 --> 05:13.533
SO THAT'S OUR STRATEGY --
JUST WAIT FOR HIM TO DROP DEAD?

05:13.580 --> 05:15.775
HE HAS TO TAKE A PILL
EVERY DAY.

05:15.810 --> 05:17.641
IS THERE ANY WAY
YOU CAN FIND OUT

05:17.680 --> 05:19.443
GIA GOODMAN'S CELLPHONE
ACCESS CODE?

05:19.480 --> 05:20.947
GIA'S CELL?

05:20.980 --> 05:22.789
WOODY'S LAWYER IS ALSO
AN OLD COLLEGE BUDDY OF HIS.

05:22.820 --> 05:24.549
IF HE'D CALL ANYONE,
IT WOULD BE HIM.

05:24.590 --> 05:26.751
IF WE HAD GIA'S CODE
AND COULD FORWARD HER CALLS...

05:26.790 --> 05:29.281
I GUARANTEE YOU
SHE HASN'T CHANGED IT

05:29.320 --> 05:30.628
FROM THE FACTORY DEFAULT.

05:30.660 --> 05:32.525
THEN I HAVE A PLAN.

05:32.560 --> 05:35.028
[ ALARM BEEPING ]

05:40.140 --> 05:42.267
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

05:42.300 --> 05:43.608
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

05:43.640 --> 05:45.801
UP AND AT 'EM, HONEY.

05:45.840 --> 05:49.606
CAN YOU BELIEVE THE BIG DAY
IS FINALLY HERE?

05:56.790 --> 05:58.917
THERE SHE IS.

05:58.950 --> 06:03.023
THE EYES ARE BRIGHT,
THE TAIL IS BUSHY.

06:03.930 --> 06:04.954
PANCAKES, MOM?

06:04.990 --> 06:07.390
ARE YOU TRYING TO GIVE ME
AN EARLY JUMP

06:07.430 --> 06:08.658
ON THE FRESHMAN 15?

06:08.700 --> 06:10.167
[ CHUCKLES ] EAT UP.

06:10.200 --> 06:12.293
YOU THINK THE DINING HALLS
AT SAN DIEGO STATE

06:12.330 --> 06:14.036
ARE GONNA FEED YOU
LIKE THIS?

06:14.070 --> 06:18.006
MMM...I LOVE PANCAKES!

06:21.910 --> 06:24.845
WHAT, A COMMENT?
"GET A ROOM"?

06:24.880 --> 06:26.518
YOU JUST GAGGED
IN YOUR MOUTH?

06:26.550 --> 06:27.778
[ GIGGLES ]

06:27.820 --> 06:29.412
NO.

06:29.450 --> 06:30.940
IT'S NICE.

06:33.060 --> 06:34.311
ARE YOU OKAY?

06:34.360 --> 06:36.578
ALL RIGHT.

06:36.630 --> 06:38.951
SO, HOW'S
THE SHERIFF BUSINESS?

06:38.990 --> 06:40.093
PRE'ITY SWEET.

06:40.130 --> 06:43.065
WE GOT OTIS SLEEPING IT OFF
IN CELL ONE,

06:43.100 --> 06:44.419
AND LAMB HAS TO WEAR

06:44.470 --> 06:46.199
THE CLETE THE CRIME-FIGHTING
CANINE COSTUME

06:46.230 --> 06:49.233
TO ALL THE ELEMENTARY SCHOOLS
THIS WEEK.

06:49.270 --> 06:50.828
LISTEN,
AFTER THE CEREMONY,

06:50.870 --> 06:52.474
DON'T RUN OFF WITH THAT BOY

06:52.510 --> 06:54.933
BECAUSE WE WANT
TO TAKE PICTURES...

06:54.980 --> 06:56.072
AND LOTS OF THEM.

06:56.110 --> 06:57.941
AND I CAN'T WAIT.

06:57.980 --> 06:59.948
OKAY, THEN
YOU SHOULD PRACTICE.

06:59.980 --> 07:01.743
SAY "CHEESE."

07:01.780 --> 07:03.645
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

07:07.790 --> 07:10.156
THEY GAVE ME THE WRONG
CAP AND GOWN.

07:10.190 --> 07:11.487
HOW EXACTLY CAN YOU TELL?

07:11.530 --> 07:13.623
IT'S GOT SOMEONE ELSE'S
NAME ON IT?

07:13.660 --> 07:16.197
GUESS WHO'S GOING
COMMAN DO?

07:16.230 --> 07:17.458
MUST WE?

07:17.500 --> 07:18.899
DOES ANYONE KNOW
WALLACE FENNEL?

07:18.930 --> 07:21.194
I DO.
HE WAS IN MY P.E. CLASS.

07:21.240 --> 07:22.366
AWESOME BALLER.

07:22.400 --> 07:23.936
I THINK HE WORKS
AT SAC-N-PAC.

07:23.970 --> 07:26.507
AWESOME BALLER --
THAT DOESN'T REALLY HELP ME.

07:26.540 --> 07:27.871
CAN YOU POINT HIM OUT?

07:27.910 --> 07:29.502
YOU DIDN'T HEAR
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM?

07:29.550 --> 07:31.040
SAC-N-PAC GOT HELD UP
WHEN HE WAS WORKING.

07:31.080 --> 07:33.514
THE ROBBER FORCED HIM
INTO THE WALK-IN COOLER.

07:33.550 --> 07:35.745
HE GOT FROSTBITE.

07:35.780 --> 07:37.645
DUDE LOST THREE FINGERS.

07:37.690 --> 07:39.988
OH, MY GOD, THAT'S AWFUL.

07:40.020 --> 07:41.988
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

07:42.990 --> 07:44.287
SWEETIE, I LOVE YOU,

07:44.330 --> 07:46.594
BUT YOU HAVE TO BE THE MOST
GULLIBLE GIRL I'VE EVER MET.

07:46.630 --> 07:48.598
I'M TRUSTING. SUE ME.

07:48.630 --> 07:50.564
THERE HE IS.
THAT'S WALLACE.

07:53.540 --> 07:56.191
WALLACE?

07:56.240 --> 07:57.229
WALLACE.

07:57.270 --> 07:58.498
YEAH?

07:58.540 --> 08:00.770
I THINK I HAVE
YOUR CAP AND GOWN.

08:00.810 --> 08:03.142
THAT MUST MAKE YOU
VERONICA MARS?

08:03.180 --> 08:05.000
IT DOES.

08:05.050 --> 08:08.816
SO, LOOKING FORWARD
TO GETTING OUT OF HERE?

08:08.850 --> 08:11.387
I GUESS.
I DON'T KNOW.

08:11.420 --> 08:14.253
HIGH SCHOOL WAS A BLAST,
RIGHT?

08:14.290 --> 08:16.679
OH, YOU'RE ONE OF THOSE.

08:16.730 --> 08:18.550
WHAT'S THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

08:18.590 --> 08:21.525
NOTHING.
HAVE A GOOD LIFE.

08:21.560 --> 08:23.164
I'M SURE YOU WILL.

08:30.110 --> 08:31.304
LILLY?

08:31.340 --> 08:33.331
HEY!

08:34.080 --> 08:37.299
TELL ME ABOUT EVERYTHING.
TELL ME ABOUT THIS NEW GUY.

08:37.350 --> 08:38.408
TELL ME ABOUT VASSAR.

08:38.450 --> 08:39.542
THE GUY IS GONE.

08:39.580 --> 08:40.740
WE HAD A LITTLE
DISAGREEMENT

08:40.780 --> 08:42.475
OVER FOOLING AROUND
WITH HIS EX.

08:42.520 --> 08:43.885
THAT BASTARD.

08:43.920 --> 08:46.184
OH, NO, NO,
IT WAS, UM, IT WAS ME.

08:46.220 --> 08:47.585
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:47.620 --> 08:49.178
I KIND OF FOOLED AROUND
WITH HIS EX.

08:49.220 --> 08:51.859
I MEAN, YOU'D THINK THAT GUYS
WOULD DIG THAT, RIGHT?

08:51.890 --> 08:57.192
WHAT? IT'S COLLEGE.
IT'S EXPECTED.

08:57.230 --> 08:58.595
YOU'LL SEE.

08:58.630 --> 09:01.190
GOD, IT'S SO GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

09:01.240 --> 09:03.868
WHAT IS THIS?

09:03.910 --> 09:07.277
A LILLY KANE
MEMORIAL FOUNTAIN?

09:07.310 --> 09:08.379
UH...

09:08.410 --> 09:09.536
DO YOU SMELL BACON?

09:09.580 --> 09:10.945
[ DOOR OPENS ]

09:10.980 --> 09:12.971
Keith: GRADUATION DAY!
GET UP!

09:13.020 --> 09:13.839
LOTS TO DO!

09:13.880 --> 09:15.916
I'M MAKING BREAKFAST.

09:21.390 --> 09:25.349
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

09:25.390 --> 09:31.124
* BUT I HAVEN'T THOUGHT OF YOU
LATELY AT ALL *

09:31.770 --> 09:33.829
* COME ON, NOW, SUGAR

09:33.870 --> 09:36.031
* BRING IT ON, BRING IT ON,
YEAH *

09:36.070 --> 09:39.904
* JUST REMEMBER ME WHEN

09:39.940 --> 09:44.741
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS
A LONG TIME AGO *

09:44.780 --> 09:47.010
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS

09:47.050 --> 09:50.611
-- Captions by VITAC --
www.vitac.com

09:58.360 --> 10:00.248
GET READY.

10:00.300 --> 10:01.722
MORNING, MR. LEE.

10:01.760 --> 10:03.660
GIA GOODMAN ASKED YOU
TO CALL HER ON HER CELL.

10:03.700 --> 10:06.260
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
I GOT THE NUMBER.

10:15.180 --> 10:16.772
GIA? BILL LEE.

10:16.810 --> 10:20.041
Veronica: Hey, so, I'm trying
to get a message to Dad,

10:20.080 --> 10:21.672
BUT HE DIDN'T LEAVE
US A FORWARDING...

10:21.720 --> 10:23.039
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

10:23.090 --> 10:25.479
IT'S JUST, WE GOT A CALL
FROM DR. HOOVER,

10:27.560 --> 10:29.687
ARE 5O MILLI-SOMETHING
THIS TIME,

10:29.730 --> 10:30.651
INSTEAD OF 100,

10:30.690 --> 10:31.782
so he has to take two.

10:31.830 --> 10:33.149
It's really important.

10:33.200 --> 10:35.293
Got it, Gia.
I'll see what I can do.

10:35.330 --> 10:37.195
Take care, honey.

10:37.230 --> 10:39.391
[ DIALING ]

10:42.400 --> 10:43.958
Woman: Quail Creek Lodge?

10:44.010 --> 10:46.831
I need to leave a message
for Mr. Underhill, please.

10:46.880 --> 10:49.269
[ DIALING ]

10:53.220 --> 10:54.517
BINGO.

10:54.550 --> 10:57.087
[ INSTRUMENTS TUNING ]

11:00.820 --> 11:02.651
AFTER YOU TALKED
TO WOODY'S LAWYER,

11:02.690 --> 11:06.080
HE IMMEDIATELY CALLED A NUMBER
FOR QUAIL CREEK LODGE,

11:06.130 --> 11:07.654
20 MILES OUTSIDE OF RENO.

11:07.700 --> 11:09.452
IT'S A STOCKED
HUNTING RANCH.

11:09.500 --> 11:12.833
RICH BUSINESSMEN
SHOOTING CAPTIVE BIRDS.

11:12.870 --> 11:14.064
YOU THINK WOODY'S THERE?

11:14.100 --> 11:15.328
I CHECKED GOOGLE EARTH.

11:15.370 --> 11:17.736
SATELLITE PHOTOS
SHOW A LANDING STRIP

11:17.770 --> 11:20.079
AND A BUILDING BIG ENOUGH
TO HOLD A PLANE.

11:20.110 --> 11:22.806
I'M ON A FLIGHT TO RENO LEAVING
AN HOUR AFTER GRADUATION.

11:22.850 --> 11:24.545
I DON'T KNOW
IF I LIKE THE IDEA

11:24.580 --> 11:25.808
OF YOU RUNNING
AROUND A PLACE

11:25.850 --> 11:27.545
FULL OF ARMED,
DRUNK BUSINESSMEN.

11:27.580 --> 11:30.287
THAT'S WHY I RARELY
GO TO TEXAS.

11:30.320 --> 11:32.379
I'LL BE FINE.

11:34.260 --> 11:36.956
I'LL CALL AS SOON
AS I HAVE HIM.

11:48.900 --> 11:53.337
[ BAND PLAYING
"POMP AND CIRCUMSTANCE" ]

11:53.380 --> 11:55.302
JOHN ENCHOFF.

11:55.340 --> 11:57.479
[ LIGHT APPLAUSE ]

12:00.380 --> 12:01.347
WALLACE FENNEL.

12:01.380 --> 12:02.779
Girl: WHOO!

12:05.450 --> 12:06.917
WHOO!

12:06.960 --> 12:10.259
[ WHISTLING AND APPLAUSE ]

12:10.290 --> 12:11.928
WHOO-HOO!

12:13.130 --> 12:14.597
GUESS WHAT?
WHAT?

12:14.630 --> 12:17.724
BEAVER GOT US A ROOM AT
THE NEPTUNE GRAND FOR TONIGHT.

12:17.770 --> 12:19.726
OOH-LA-LA!

12:19.770 --> 12:21.135
ANY ADVICE?

12:21.170 --> 12:22.808
CLOSE YOUR EYES
AND THINK OF ENGLAND?

12:23.470 --> 12:25.461
JUST RELAX.

12:25.510 --> 12:27.432
[ APPLAUSE ]

12:30.050 --> 12:33.019
[ PRINCIPAL VAN CLEMMONS
SPEAKING INDISTINCT LY ]

12:33.050 --> 12:34.938
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

12:43.530 --> 12:44.679
ELI NAVARRO,

12:44.730 --> 12:46.220
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST

12:46.260 --> 12:48.490
IN CONNECTION WITH THE MURDER
OF EDUARDO OROZCO.

12:48.530 --> 12:49.963
NO, MAN.

12:50.000 --> 12:51.763
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

12:51.800 --> 12:53.165
NOT HERE.
ANYTHING YOU SAY...

12:53.200 --> 12:54.462
JUST GIVE ME 10 MINUTES,
OKAY?

12:54.500 --> 12:56.138
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY.

12:56.170 --> 12:58.263
IF YOU CANNOT AFFORD AN --
JUST LET ME GRADUATE!

12:58.310 --> 13:00.232
...ONE MAY BE APPOINTED
FOR YOU.

13:00.280 --> 13:02.805
DO YOU UNDERSTAND
THESE RIGHTS?

13:04.480 --> 13:06.471
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS, MAN.

13:06.510 --> 13:09.217
CUFF HIM.
LET'S GET HIM OUT OF HERE.

13:09.250 --> 13:10.512
HEY, HEY.

13:10.550 --> 13:13.553
YOU WANT TO DO THIS
THE HARD WAY, HUH?

13:13.590 --> 13:16.184
[ WHISTLING AND APPLAUSE ]

13:23.000 --> 13:25.059
LET'S GO.

13:29.340 --> 13:31.331
Principal Van Clemmons:
CINDY MACKENZIE.

13:34.510 --> 13:36.375
SCOTT MARKHAM.

13:36.410 --> 13:38.207
[ LIGHT APPLAUSE ]

13:40.080 --> 13:42.219
VERONICA MARS.

13:42.250 --> 13:44.616
YES! YES!

13:44.650 --> 13:47.312
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

13:53.430 --> 13:54.419
WHOO!

13:54.460 --> 13:56.155
ALL RIGHT, "V"!

14:00.400 --> 14:03.062
YOU WERE EXPECTING
SOME OTHER REACTION?

14:03.110 --> 14:04.338
1--

14:04.370 --> 14:05.962
I CAN'T DECIDE IF MY LIFE
IS GONNA BE EASIER

14:06.010 --> 14:07.705
OR MORE DIFFICULT
WITH YOU GONE.

14:07.740 --> 14:09.173
ANYTHING I SHOULD KNOW

14:09.210 --> 14:10.802
IN CASE I GET ANOTHER ONE
LIKE YOU SOMEDAY?

14:10.850 --> 14:12.499
DON'T KEEP
ALL YOUR PASSWORDS

14:12.550 --> 14:14.973
TAPED ON THE BOTTOM
OF YOUR STAPLER.

14:15.020 --> 14:17.318
AND STAY COOL, MR. C.

14:22.520 --> 14:23.828
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:23.860 --> 14:28.024
FOR YOU ON THIS
MOMENTOUS OCCASION.

14:29.460 --> 14:31.496
[ SNIFFING ]

14:31.530 --> 14:33.191
A PONY?!

14:36.370 --> 14:37.735
NEW YORK?

14:37.770 --> 14:39.499
WE LEAVE TUESDAY.

14:39.540 --> 14:42.236
BROADWAY? SOHO? THE MOMA?

14:42.280 --> 14:45.545
YANKEE STADIUM, SHEA STADIUM,
MADISON SQUARE GARDEN.

14:45.580 --> 14:47.548
OH, THANK YOU SO MUCH!

14:47.580 --> 14:49.616
THIS IS AWESOME!

14:49.650 --> 14:51.743
OH! AWESOME.

14:51.790 --> 14:53.280
NOW GO CATCH WOODY.

14:53.320 --> 14:55.515
I GET CREEPED OUT JUST KNOWING
HE'S OUT THERE SOMEWHERE.

14:55.560 --> 14:56.584
YOU HAVE FUN TONIGHT.

14:56.620 --> 14:57.780
THAT'S THE PLAN.

14:57.830 --> 14:59.559
PUT ON YOUR DANCING SHOES,
MARS,

14:59.590 --> 15:02.297
'CAUSE TONIGHT
WE'RE GONNA UPCHUCK THE BOOGIE

15:02.330 --> 15:04.696
TO THE RHYTHM OF THE BOOGIE,
THE BEAT.

15:04.730 --> 15:06.891
"UPCHUCK"?

15:06.940 --> 15:07.793
YOU HEARD ME.

15:07.840 --> 15:10.058
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

15:18.910 --> 15:22.141
VERONICA,
DO YOU KNOW ABOUT THIS?

15:22.180 --> 15:24.148
I DON'T. WHAT'S WRONG?

15:24.190 --> 15:26.613
WALLACE LEFT THIS NOTE FOR ME
ON MY WINDSHIELD.

15:26.650 --> 15:28.880
HE'S BOOKED HIMSELF A FLIGHT
TO PARIS.

15:28.920 --> 15:31.229
HE'S GONNA TRY TO TRACK DOWN
JACKIE.

15:42.500 --> 15:45.628
MOMMY! MOMMY!

15:46.710 --> 15:48.871
YOU'RE 10 MINUTES LATE.

15:48.910 --> 15:50.275
CUT ME SOME SLACK, MA.

15:50.310 --> 15:53.040
I HAVEN'T EVEN BEEN BACK
TWO DAYS.

15:53.080 --> 15:55.275
JACKIE,
YOU AIN'T IN NEPTUNE NO MORE.

15:55.320 --> 15:57.811
TERRENCE COOK FANTASY CAMP
IS OVER.

15:57.850 --> 15:59.545
THIS IS REAL LIFE.

15:59.590 --> 16:01.956
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

16:01.990 --> 16:04.550
BROOKLYN DAN'S?

16:04.590 --> 16:07.559
YEAH. HOLD ON.

16:07.600 --> 16:08.953
IT'S FOR YOU.

16:15.540 --> 16:16.893
HELLO?

16:16.940 --> 16:18.760
Veronica :_
What, no "bonJour"?

16:18.810 --> 16:20.107
VERONICA?

16:20.140 --> 16:21.505
How did you know?

16:21.540 --> 16:26.739
WELL, FIRST, 3.1 GPA
DOESN'T SCREAM THE SORBONNE.

16:26.780 --> 16:28.475
AND THE JAVA JOB --

16:28.520 --> 16:30.385
YOU'RE A MIGHTY GOOD
SERVICE-INDUSTRY WORKER

16:30.420 --> 16:31.887
FOR THE DAUGHTER
OF A MODEL

16:31.920 --> 16:33.080
LIVING ON
THE UPPER WEST SIDE

16:33.120 --> 16:34.587
WHO NEVER HELD A JOB
BEFORE.

16:34.620 --> 16:35.985
I've known for a while.

16:36.020 --> 16:37.556
LOOK, I MIGHT HAVE LIED
ABOUT MY LIFE,

16:37.590 --> 16:40.593
BUT I SWEAR I NEVER LIED
TO WALLACE ABOUT HOW I FELT.

16:40.630 --> 16:41.858
WHATEVER YOU TOLD HIM,

16:41.900 --> 16:43.197
IT REALLY DID THE TRICK

16:43.230 --> 16:45.494
BECAUSE HE JUST GOT ON A PLANE
TO PARIS.

16:45.530 --> 16:49.864
But the good news is he has
a 4-hour layover at JFK,

16:49.900 --> 16:51.436
SO YOU CAN GO TELL HIM
THE TRUTH

16:51.470 --> 16:54.075
BEFORE HE'S FORCED TO ENDURE
SEVERAL UGLY DAYS

16:54.110 --> 16:56.431
of rude waiters
for nothing.

17:02.150 --> 17:04.482
Aaron: HELLO, LOGAN.

17:05.150 --> 17:07.380
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

17:07.420 --> 17:10.082
WELL,
I NEED A PLACE TO STAY.

17:10.130 --> 17:11.586
HOW ARE THE SUITES?

17:11.630 --> 17:14.929
WELL, PROBABLY AN IMPROVEMENT
OVER YOUR PREVIOUS DIGS.

17:14.960 --> 17:16.598
MIGHT BE A LITTLE WEIRD,
THOUGH.

17:16.630 --> 17:19.997
I DON'T THINK ANY OF THE OTHER
GUESTS KILLED ANYONE.

17:20.030 --> 17:22.169
YOU KNOW...

17:22.200 --> 17:24.134
YOU SHOULD REALLY MAKE
MORE OF AN EFFORT

17:24.170 --> 17:25.831
TO BE CIVIL TO ME NOW,
LOGAN.

17:25.870 --> 17:27.406
WHY? BECAUSE YOU BEAT
A MURDER RAP

17:27.440 --> 17:29.499
AND SUDDENLY
YOU'RE MY FATHER AGAIN?

17:29.540 --> 17:31.474
NO, LOGAN.

17:31.510 --> 17:34.673
I NEVER STOPPED BEING YOUR
FATHER, AND I NEVER WILL.

17:35.380 --> 17:38.042
BUT I GOT
THE PURSE STRINGS BACK.

17:38.090 --> 17:40.183
YOU'RE MY DEPENDENT AGAIN,
SON.

17:40.220 --> 17:41.881
[ ELEVATOR DINGS ]

17:41.920 --> 17:43.012
GOING DOWN?

17:43.060 --> 17:44.550
NO. UP.

17:52.800 --> 17:54.461
B0: MARIJUANA?

17:54.500 --> 17:56.092
SURE GOT OURSELVES IN A HEAP
OF TROUBLE THIS TIME.

17:56.140 --> 17:58.335
YOU GOT THAT RIGHT. BOSS
IS GONNA THROW THE BOOK AT US.

17:58.370 --> 18:00.179
NOT TO MENTION
THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT.

18:00.210 --> 18:03.099
WHEN WE BREAK OUR PROBATION,
WE SURE DO A BANG-UP JOB OF IT.

18:03.150 --> 18:04.572
WE OUGHT TO BE
OUT OF PRISON

18:04.610 --> 18:06.976
ABOUT IN TIME TO COLLECT
SOCIAL SECURITY.

18:07.010 --> 18:08.443
IT AIN'T FUNNY, LUKE.

18:08.480 --> 18:10.448
WE GOT TO GET OURSELVES
OUT OF THIS.

18:17.230 --> 18:18.652
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

18:18.690 --> 18:20.499
OW!

18:22.830 --> 18:25.526
[ DIALING ]

18:27.600 --> 18:32.799
YEAH, CAN YOU PUT ME THROUGH TO
THE LOCAL SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT?

18:41.080 --> 18:43.219
SO, YOU USED ME.

18:43.250 --> 18:44.888
SOMEONE BLACKMAILS YOU,

18:44.920 --> 18:46.182
AND YOU USE ME TO SET UP

18:46.220 --> 18:48.279
THE WHOLE
GIRL-IN-THE-MOTEL THING.

18:48.320 --> 18:49.719
INCORPORATION DIES,

18:49.760 --> 18:52.422
AND YOUR SPECIAL SECRETS
STAY HIDDEN.

18:52.460 --> 18:54.223
KEITH,
I KNOW HOW THIS MUST LOOK.

18:54.260 --> 18:55.625
IF YOU'RE ABOUT TO INSIST

18:55.660 --> 18:57.821
THIS IS ALL SOME BIG
MISUNDERSTANDING, WOODY,

18:57.870 --> 18:58.962
I KIND OF THINK YOU DON'T.

18:59.000 --> 19:00.297
I DIDN'T CRASH THE BUS.

19:00.340 --> 19:02.137
I COULD NEVER HAVE HURT
ALL THOSE KIDS.

19:02.170 --> 19:03.205
I DON'T KNOW, WOODY.

19:03.240 --> 19:04.832
THE WELFARE OF CHILDREN

19:04.870 --> 19:07.373
DOESN'T SEEM TO HAVE BEEN
TERRIBLY HIGH ON YOUR LIST.

19:07.410 --> 19:10.174
THAT'S NOT HOW IT WAS.
IT WASN'T THAT WAY AT ALL.

19:10.210 --> 19:13.247
THOSE BOYS --
IF YOU KNEW THEIR FATHERS,

19:13.280 --> 19:15.316
HOW THEY IGNORED THEM,
MISTREATED THEM.

19:15.350 --> 19:18.012
THEY NEEDED SOMEONE.
I LISTENED TO THEM.

19:18.050 --> 19:19.142
I CARED ABOUT THEM.

19:19.190 --> 19:21.715
WOODY, JUST STOP.

19:21.760 --> 19:25.389
MR. MARS, THEY'RE READY.

19:28.060 --> 19:31.166
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

19:31.200 --> 19:32.519
YOU CAUGHT HIM.

19:32.570 --> 19:34.697
LOADING HIM ONTO HIS OWN PLANE
AS WE SPEAK.

19:34.740 --> 19:38.107
AS SOON AS THE PILOT GETS HERE,
WE'LL BE HOMEWARD BOUND.

19:38.140 --> 19:39.630
DID HE CONFESS
TO THE CRASH?

19:39.670 --> 19:41.809
UNFORTUNATELY, HE INSISTS
THAT HE DIDN'T DO IT,

19:41.840 --> 19:44.604
so we're gonna need a lot more
evidence to nail him.

19:44.650 --> 19:47.414
I'M STILL TRYING TO FIND
THAT THIRD KID FROM THE TAPE.

19:47.450 --> 19:50.419
I've got everyone on the team
identified except one guy.

19:50.450 --> 19:52.315
I THINK I KNOW WHERE
TO FIND HIM, THOUGH.

19:52.350 --> 19:53.612
THE PILOT JUST GOT HERE.

19:53.660 --> 19:55.355
I'LL BE IN LATE,
SO DON'T WAIT UP.

19:55.390 --> 19:57.483
See you in the morning.

20:25.050 --> 20:28.781
AHA. DEREK APPLEGATE.

20:28.820 --> 20:32.256
WHO ARE YOU,
AND WHERE DO YOU LIVE?

20:40.170 --> 20:42.491
OH, GOD.

20:48.180 --> 20:50.000
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:50.040 --> 20:51.405
[ RINGING ]

20:51.450 --> 20:53.338
PICK UP, PICK UP, PICK UP.

20:53.380 --> 20:55.746
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

20:59.890 --> 21:02.108
It's Mac.
Leave a message.

21:02.160 --> 21:03.422
MAC, IT'S VERONICA.

21:03.460 --> 21:04.984
YOU HAVE TO GET AWAY
FROM BEAVER.

21:05.030 --> 21:06.759
DO WHATEVER YOU HAVE TO DO,
BUT GET AWAY FROM HIM.

21:06.790 --> 21:10.021
HE'S DANGEROUS.
CALL ME WHEN YOU HEAR THIS.

21:10.060 --> 21:11.095
[ BEEP ]

21:11.130 --> 21:13.530
[ DIALING ]

21:15.300 --> 21:17.700
A LISTING FOR HART HANSON?

21:17.740 --> 21:21.471
CHUG, CHUG, CHUG,
CHUG, CHUG, CHUG!

21:21.510 --> 21:23.740
OH!
THAT'S WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT!

21:23.780 --> 21:27.045
FEELS GOOD TO BE A MAN FROM
TIME TO TIME, DOES IT NOT?

21:27.080 --> 21:29.674
ENBOM, GET OVER HERE!

21:29.720 --> 21:32.041
ALL I ASK IS THAT YOU DON'T
FOLLOW THAT PERFORMANCE

21:32.090 --> 21:33.352
WITH A BELCH.

21:33.390 --> 21:35.085
DO YOU WANT TO GO CHECK OUT
THE ROOM?

21:35.120 --> 21:39.056
IT'S LIQUID. IT'S COURAGE.
IT'S LIQUID COURAGE.

21:39.090 --> 21:40.455
YEAH, WELL, THERE'S, UH,

21:40.500 --> 21:42.991
THERE'S NOTHING UP THERE
THAT I'M AFRAID OF.

21:43.030 --> 21:46.090
DID YOU HEAR?
VERONICA'S DAD CAUGHT THE MAYOR.

21:46.130 --> 21:47.563
IT'S ALL OVER THE NEWS.

21:47.600 --> 21:50.364
THEY'RE FLYING HIM OUT TONIGHT
ON WOODY'S PLANE.

21:50.410 --> 21:54.437
THAT SLEEZOID IS GONNA FRY --
BZZZZ!

21:59.210 --> 22:01.610
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

22:03.520 --> 22:07.217
* LOST IN A WORLD OF MISERY

22:07.250 --> 22:09.059
* YOU CAN'T BREAK FREE

22:09.090 --> 22:10.955
* I CAN'T UNDERSTAND

22:10.990 --> 22:12.389
HEY.

22:12.430 --> 22:14.091
HAVE YOU SEEN
BEAVER AND MAC?

22:14.130 --> 22:16.121
YEAH,
THEY WERE HERE EARLIER.

22:16.160 --> 22:18.867
I THINK BEAVER --

22:18.900 --> 22:19.969
WHAT?

22:20.000 --> 22:21.467
WHERE'S YOUR BROTHER?

22:21.500 --> 22:23.468
I THINK HE TOOK "GHOST WORLD"
UP TO HIS ROOM.

22:23.510 --> 22:25.364
THEY'RE PROBABLY UP THERE
MAKING LOVE...

22:25.410 --> 22:27.207
OR PLAYING
DUNGEONS AND DRAGONS...

22:27.240 --> 22:28.730
OR BOTH
AT THE SAME TIME.

22:28.780 --> 22:31.101
THEY'RE BOTH, LIKE,
12th-LEVEL DORKS.

22:31.150 --> 22:33.641
* I'M COMING FOR YOU

22:36.320 --> 22:38.208
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

22:38.250 --> 22:43.119
I'M HAVING A GOOD TIME,
AND WE'VE GOT ALL NIGHT, OKAY?

22:43.160 --> 22:45.526
WE'RE COOL HERE.

22:45.560 --> 22:47.391
I'M JUST GONNA HOP
IN THE SHOWER,

22:47.430 --> 22:49.955
AND THEN WE CAN HEAD BACK DOWN
TO THE PARTY.

22:52.970 --> 22:55.768
CAN YOU TELL ME WHICH ROOM
CASSIDY CASABLANCAS IS IN?

22:55.800 --> 22:57.939
I'M SORRY. WE CAN'T GIVE OUT
THAT INFORMATION.

22:57.970 --> 22:59.938
I CAN RING HIS ROOM,
IF YOU'D LIKE.

22:59.970 --> 23:01.232
SURE.

23:01.280 --> 23:02.633
I'M SORRY.

23:02.680 --> 23:05.547
THERE'S A "DO NOT DISTURB"
ON THE ROOM.

23:08.380 --> 23:10.940
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

23:35.440 --> 23:37.908
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

23:48.890 --> 23:50.187
DAMN IT.

23:50.220 --> 23:52.324
HELLO, VERONICA.

23:52.360 --> 23:54.692
WELL,
DON'T LOOK SO SURPRISED.

23:54.730 --> 23:55.924
IT'S A SMALL TOWN.

23:55.960 --> 23:57.791
NOW THAT I'M NO LONGER
IN JAIL,

23:57.830 --> 24:00.993
WE MIGHT JUST RUN INTO
EACH OTHER FROM TIME TO TIME.

24:01.040 --> 24:02.564
I'LL HAVE TO PAY
BETTER ATTENTION

24:02.600 --> 24:03.760
TO WHERE I'M GOING, THEN.

24:03.810 --> 24:05.732
WELL, IT'S A FREE COUNTRY.

24:05.770 --> 24:09.103
THOSE FOUNDING FATHERS
WERE REALLY ONTO SOMETHING.

24:09.140 --> 24:13.099
FREEDOM -- AH! --
IT'S PRETTY DAMN SWEET.

24:13.150 --> 24:15.311
I LIKE IT.

24:15.350 --> 24:18.080
SO DID LILLY.
BUMMER YOU MURDERED HER.

24:18.120 --> 24:21.214
YOU KNOW,
I CAN SEE WHY THE TWO OF YOU

24:21.260 --> 24:23.057
WERE SUCH GOOD FRIENDS.

24:23.090 --> 24:24.421
YOU'RE SO MUCH ALIKE.

24:24.460 --> 24:27.623
NOT AFRAID TO SPEAK
YOUR MINDS.

24:27.660 --> 24:29.719
YOU KNOW, THAT JUST MIGHT BE
THE BEST PART

24:29.760 --> 24:32.467
ABOUT THE DAY I SMASHED HER HEAD
IN WITH AN ASHTRAY --

24:32.500 --> 24:35.139
KNOWING THAT,
ONCE AND FOR ALL,

24:35.170 --> 24:37.502
SHE WOULD FINALLY
SHUT THE HELL UP.

24:37.540 --> 24:39.633
[ ELEVATOR DINGS ]

24:41.410 --> 24:43.640
AH. WELL...

24:43.680 --> 24:46.774
HAVE A NICE NIGHT,
VERONICA.

24:57.020 --> 24:58.453
MAC?

24:58.490 --> 25:00.822
HEY, VERONICA!

25:04.670 --> 25:06.399
WHERE'S MAC?

25:06.430 --> 25:09.137
A BETTER PLACE.

25:09.170 --> 25:11.138
UNFORTUNATELY,
SHE NEVER GOT A CHANCE

25:11.170 --> 25:12.262
TO READ YOUR MESSAGE.

25:12.310 --> 25:14.778
NOW...THROW ME YOUR BAG.

25:15.710 --> 25:17.803
I SAID THROW ME YOUR BAG!

25:31.190 --> 25:34.557
SO, "BEAVER'S A KILLER"?

25:34.600 --> 25:36.227
THAT'S A PRETTY SERIOUS
ACCUSATION.

25:36.260 --> 25:38.160
WHAT EXACTLY DO YOU THINK
YOU KNOW?

25:38.200 --> 25:40.521
YOU PLAYED FOR WOODY'S
LITTLE-LEAGUE TEAM

25:40.570 --> 25:42.538
WITH MARCOS AND PETER.

25:42.570 --> 25:44.606
HE MOLESTED
ALL THREE OF YOU.

25:44.640 --> 25:46.403
THEY WANTED
TO COME FORWARD.

25:46.440 --> 25:49.432
A COUPLE OF THE SHARKS
HAD TO KNOW ABOUT IT.

25:49.480 --> 25:50.742
THEY'LL COME FORWARD.

25:50.780 --> 25:53.101
THINGS LIKE THIS
DON'T STAY SECRET.

25:53.150 --> 25:54.515
DAMN RIGHT.

25:54.550 --> 25:56.745
BUT DO YOU GUYS REALLY WANT
PEOPLE TO KNOW ABOUT IT?

25:56.780 --> 25:58.611
HE'S A PERVERT.
HE'S SICK.

25:58.650 --> 26:00.754
AND WHAT HE DID TO US
IS WRONG.

26:00.790 --> 26:03.759
LOOK, PLEASE DON'T
DRAG ME INTO THIS.

26:03.790 --> 26:08.329
YOU'RE ALREADY IN IT.
YOU'LL THANK US LATER.

26:08.360 --> 26:10.624
Veronica: PETER AND MARCOS
WERE GOING TO SPILL.

26:10.670 --> 26:13.298
THAT'S WHY
THEY HAD TO DIE.

26:13.330 --> 26:14.638
MY GUESS?

26:14.670 --> 26:17.730
YOU GOT THE EXPLOSIVES
FROM CURLY MORAN.

26:17.770 --> 26:20.603
I SAW YOU WITH THAT SOPHOMORE
HART HANSON LAST WEEK.

26:20.640 --> 26:22.972
HART SAYS YOU WORKED ON
HIS WAR MOVIES WITH HIM,

26:23.010 --> 26:25.444
THAT YOU WERE IN CHARGE
OF BLOWING THINGS UP.

26:25.480 --> 26:28.540
HE SAID YOU KNEW A GUY
WHO TAUGHT YOU HOW TO DO IT --

26:28.580 --> 26:29.945
YOUR DAD'S MECHANIC,

26:29.980 --> 26:33.211
FORMER STUNT COORDINATOR
CURLY MORAN, RIGHT?

26:34.420 --> 26:36.012
Dick: ADMIT IT, MAN,

26:36.060 --> 26:38.278
YOU'RE WAY HAPPIER IN THE LIMO
THAN SITTING ON THE BUS,

26:38.330 --> 26:40.184
GETTING EYE DAGGERS
IN THE BACK FROM MEG.

26:40.230 --> 26:43.859
I'D HAVE BEEN HAPPIER IF
YOU HADN'T HAD THAT CHILI DOG.

26:45.830 --> 26:51.359
* THE MORNING LIGHT
IS BURNING BRIGHT *

26:51.410 --> 26:52.809
[ EXPLOSION, SCREAMING ]

26:52.840 --> 26:55.570
CURLY TOLD WEEVIL THAT HE KNEW
WHO BLEW UP THE BUS.

26:55.610 --> 26:57.498
HE FIGURED IT OUT,
DIDN'T HE?

26:57.540 --> 26:59.770
THAT'S WHY
YOU NEEDED HIM GONE.

26:59.810 --> 27:01.539
YOU KNOW CERVANDO'S
BEEN BRAGGING

27:01.580 --> 27:03.138
ABOUT HUSTLING
LIAM FITZPATRICK,

27:03.180 --> 27:07.116
SO YOU CONVINCED THE P.C.H.ers
THAT CURLY BLEW UP THE BUS.

27:09.020 --> 27:11.056
YO!

27:11.090 --> 27:13.388
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER, REVS ]

27:13.430 --> 27:16.319
COME ON, MAN, LET'S GO!
COME ON, MAN!

27:19.700 --> 27:22.191
BUT YOU HAVE TO FINISH
THE JOB.

27:22.240 --> 27:24.128
[ TIRES SCREECHING ]

27:30.210 --> 27:33.976
* TELL IT'S ME
BY THE CLAMOR, NOW, BABY *

27:34.020 --> 27:36.272
YOU WANTED TO FOCUS
ANY INVESTIGATION

27:36.320 --> 27:37.469
IN A DIFFERENT DIRECTION.

27:37.520 --> 27:38.782
YOU KNEW I WAS
A KEY WITNESS

27:38.820 --> 27:40.617
IN THE AARON ECHOLLS TRIAL,
SO...

27:40.650 --> 27:43.380
* YOU KNOW I'M HERE TO STAY

27:43.420 --> 27:47.459
* GOT YOU IN A STRANGLEHOLD,
BABY *

27:47.490 --> 27:48.752
CONVENIENT, WASN'T IT?

27:48.800 --> 27:51.724
THE ROAD HOG'S
CLIFFSIDE LOCATION?

27:51.770 --> 27:54.238
EASY TO DUMP THE BODY.

27:55.900 --> 27:57.834
YOU DIDN'T HIRE ME
TO CATCH KENDALL

27:57.870 --> 27:59.633
CHEATING ON YOUR DAD,
DID YOU?

27:59.670 --> 28:01.171
YOU KNEW WHAT HE WAS UP TO,

28:01.210 --> 28:03.747
AND YOU WANTED TO PUNISH HIM
FOR THE WAY HE TREATED YOU.

28:03.780 --> 28:05.008
YOU USED ME TO DO IT.

28:05.050 --> 28:07.678
AND YOU WERE MARVELOUS.

28:07.720 --> 28:10.314
NOW LET ME ASK YOU
SOMETHING.

28:10.350 --> 28:11.908
HOW IS IT I GOT CHLAMYDIA?

28:11.950 --> 28:15.852
WOODY WAS TREATED FOR IT.
I ENDED UP WITH IT.

28:15.890 --> 28:18.051
SHELLY POMROY'S PARTY,
SOPHOMORE YEAR.

28:18.090 --> 28:20.991
YOU SAID DICK PUSHED YOU
INTO A ROOM WITH ME

28:21.030 --> 28:22.520
AFTER I'D BEEN ROOFIED,

28:22.560 --> 28:25.461
BUT YOU DIDN'T RUN OUT LIKE
YOU SAID YOU DID, DID YOU?

28:25.500 --> 28:26.865
NOPE.

28:26.900 --> 28:28.993
YOU WANTED TO PROVE
YOU WERE A MAN.

28:29.040 --> 28:31.861
IT HELPED THAT I WAS
UNCONSCIOUS, DIDN'T IT?

28:31.910 --> 28:35.869
EASY TO IMAGINE WHATEVER IT IS
YOU NEEDED TO IMAGINE.

28:37.380 --> 28:39.371
YOU RAPED ME!

28:39.410 --> 28:41.412
AND DICK STILL THINKS
I'M A VIRGIN.

28:41.450 --> 28:45.011
SEE, I KNOW HOW TO KEEP
A SECRET.

28:45.050 --> 28:47.416
THAT'S WHAT THIS IS ALL ABOUT,
ISN'T IT --

28:47.450 --> 28:48.712
KEEPING YOUR SECRET?

28:48.760 --> 28:50.079
WELL, IT'S OVER.
IT'S OUT. I KNOW.

28:50.120 --> 28:52.020
YEAH, BUT I HAVE
A PRETTY GOOD FEELING

28:52.060 --> 28:53.789
THAT YOU WON'T BE TELLING
ANYBODY.

28:53.830 --> 28:56.355
I ALREADY DID.
I TOLD MY DAD.

28:56.400 --> 28:57.549
HE KNOWS.

28:57.600 --> 28:58.919
THAT'S, UH,
THAT'S TOO BAD.

28:58.970 --> 29:01.234
HE'S ON WOODY'S PLANE
WITH HIM, RIGHT?

29:01.270 --> 29:02.862
RIGHT NOW
ON HIS WAY BACK?

29:02.900 --> 29:04.959
BECAUSE I HAVE NO MORE USE
FOR WOODY.

29:05.010 --> 29:07.262
YOU HEARD ABOUT THE BOMB
IN WOODY'S CAR, RIGHT?

29:07.310 --> 29:10.234
YEAH, 'CAUSE THERE'S ONE
ON HIS PLANE,

29:10.280 --> 29:14.273
AND ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS DIAL.

29:16.450 --> 29:17.417
[ CHUCKLES ]

29:17.450 --> 29:18.849
WANT TO CALL YOUR DAD,

29:18.890 --> 29:20.448
SAY GOODBYE
BEFORE I PRESS SEND, GO AHEAD.

29:20.490 --> 29:21.650
I'LL GIVE YOU A MINUTE.

29:21.690 --> 29:25.478
CASSIDY,
NO, YOU'RE NOT SERIOUS.

29:25.530 --> 29:29.193
56...55...

29:29.230 --> 29:32.097
TICKTOCK.
[ DIALING ]

29:36.440 --> 29:38.328
[ SOBS ]

29:38.370 --> 29:40.031
PICK UP.

29:40.070 --> 29:42.174
PLEASE PICK UP.

29:44.280 --> 29:45.838
DADDY.

29:55.420 --> 29:57.354
[ EXPLOSION ]

29:58.890 --> 30:01.393
WHAT DO YOU KNOW?

30:07.400 --> 30:09.891
[ SOBBING ]

30:18.880 --> 30:20.438
[ SIREN WAILS IN DISTANCE ]

30:20.480 --> 30:23.779
YEAH, SORRY ABOUT THAT.

30:23.820 --> 30:27.119
I KNOW THIS MIGHT BE
A BAD TIME

30:27.150 --> 30:28.754
TO ASK FOR A FAVOR.

30:28.790 --> 30:30.155
HOW WOULD YOU FEEL

30:30.190 --> 30:33.159
NOW THAT YOU'VE GOT
NOTHING LEFT TO LIVE FOR

30:33.190 --> 30:36.648
ABOUT JUST
ROLLING YOURSELF OFF?

30:36.700 --> 30:40.466
I REALLY DON'T WANT YOUR DNA
ALL OVER MY SHIRT.

30:40.500 --> 30:43.060
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

30:43.100 --> 30:46.263
Man: IN A MINUTE, KALEE.
DADDY'S ON THE PHONE.

30:46.310 --> 30:48.972
Woman: I'M GONNA BE IN YOUR
NEIGHBORHOOD WITH MY DAUGHTER.

30:49.010 --> 30:50.307
HOW ABOUT
WE, UM, DROP BY?

30:50.340 --> 30:52.001
THAT WAY OUR DAUGHTERS
CAN MEET.

30:52.050 --> 30:56.214
UH...YOUR --
WELL, MY PLACE IS A MESS.

30:56.250 --> 30:58.844
I SURE LIKE THIS THING.

30:58.890 --> 31:00.812
EVER WONDER
WHAT IT FEELS LIKE

31:00.850 --> 31:03.455
TO THE PEOPLE
YOU ACTUALLY TASER?

31:03.490 --> 31:05.026
LET'S GIVE IT A WHIRL.

31:05.060 --> 31:06.322
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

31:06.360 --> 31:08.749
YOU KNOW WHAT I WAS
JUST THINKING?

31:08.800 --> 31:10.358
WE'RE NEPTUNE PIRATES,
RIGHT?

31:10.400 --> 31:12.527
THIS IS LIKE I'M MAKING YOU
WALK THE PLANK.

31:12.570 --> 31:14.891
EXCEPT INSTEAD OF JABBING YOU
WITH A SWORD,

31:14.940 --> 31:18.307
I'M SENDING 300,000 VOLTS
THROUGH YOU.

31:18.340 --> 31:20.706
NOW JUMP.
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

31:20.740 --> 31:23.470
PLEASE DON'T!

31:23.510 --> 31:25.102
[ SIGHS ]

31:25.150 --> 31:27.641
YOU COULDN'T DO THIS
THE EASY WAY?

31:27.680 --> 31:29.477
YOU KNOW, AARON ECHOLLS
IS STAYING HERE.

31:29.520 --> 31:31.784
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO BET
THAT I CAN GET HIM CONVICTED

31:31.820 --> 31:33.617
FOR THE DEATH
OF THIS TEENAGE GIRL?

31:33.650 --> 31:34.856
NO!

31:34.890 --> 31:37.552
[ GUNSHOT ]

31:53.540 --> 31:55.508
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

31:57.980 --> 32:00.073
LOGAN, MOVE AWAY FROM HIM.

32:00.110 --> 32:03.079
VERONICA, NO.

32:03.120 --> 32:06.044
HE KILLED MY FATHER!

32:07.250 --> 32:08.786
GIVE ME THE GUN, VERONICA.

32:09.690 --> 32:13.649
HE KILLED EVERYONE ON THE BUS.
HE RAPED ME!

32:15.460 --> 32:18.099
YOU ARE NOT A KILLER,
VERONICA.

32:19.200 --> 32:20.861
GIVE ME THE GUN.

32:20.900 --> 32:22.037
[ SOBS ]

32:22.070 --> 32:24.664
YOU'RE NOT A KILLER,
VERONICA.

32:26.910 --> 32:29.231
GIVE ME THE GUN.

32:43.190 --> 32:45.829
* SEE MY FRIENDS

32:45.860 --> 32:46.986
BEAVER, DON'T!

32:47.030 --> 32:50.488
MY NAME IS CASSIDY!

32:50.530 --> 32:52.760
CASSIDY, DON'T.

32:52.800 --> 32:54.097
WHY NOT?

32:54.140 --> 32:58.008
* LAYIN' ACROSS A RIVER

32:58.040 --> 33:00.133
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT.

33:00.170 --> 33:03.708
* SEE MY FRIENDS

33:04.650 --> 33:07.244
[ GLASS SHATTERS,
CAR ALARM BLARES ]

33:09.180 --> 33:14.459
* LAYIN' ACROSS A RIVER

33:14.490 --> 33:16.355
[ SOBS ]

33:16.390 --> 33:20.258
* SHE IS GONE

33:20.290 --> 33:21.723
MAC.

33:21.760 --> 33:23.819
MAC!

33:24.600 --> 33:30.163
* AND NOW THERE'S NO ONE LEFT

33:30.200 --> 33:35.035
* EXCEPT MY FRIENDS

33:36.310 --> 33:39.939
HE TOOK MY CLOTHES.

33:39.980 --> 33:42.744
HE TOOK EVERYTHING.

33:44.090 --> 33:46.308
WHY?

33:49.220 --> 33:53.122
* SHE JUST WENT

33:53.160 --> 33:56.027
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

33:56.060 --> 33:59.666
OH...MY...GOD.

33:59.700 --> 34:02.260
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

34:05.170 --> 34:12.076
HAVE I TOLD YOU
HOW MUCH I LOVE FREEDOM?

34:12.110 --> 34:14.374
I LIKE IT, TOO.

34:14.420 --> 34:17.548
AND ANY MORE "FREEDOMING"
TONIGHT,

34:17.580 --> 34:20.219
AND I'M GONNA NEED
A WHEELCHAIR.

34:29.530 --> 34:30.997
AHH.

34:31.030 --> 34:33.260
[ WATER RUNNING ]

34:51.820 --> 34:53.549
WELL, WELL, WELL.

34:53.590 --> 34:55.148
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:55.920 --> 34:58.718
WHO'S THAT HANDSOME FELLA?

34:59.430 --> 35:02.490
[ SLOW MUSIC PLAYS ]

35:19.310 --> 35:21.778
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

35:25.150 --> 35:26.686
C.W.?

35:26.720 --> 35:28.483
IT'S A DONE DEAL.

35:50.010 --> 35:52.399
HEY, WALLACE.

35:56.850 --> 35:59.387
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

35:59.420 --> 36:02.548
YOU HEADING TO PARIS?
WHAT A COINCIDENCE.

36:02.590 --> 36:03.818
ME TOO.

36:03.860 --> 36:05.748
I'M NOT GOING TO PARIS.

36:05.790 --> 36:08.793
THIS IS FOR
THE PHILLY SHUTTLE.

36:08.830 --> 36:12.664
CHEAPEST TICKET I COULD GET
TO BYPASS SECURITY.

36:12.700 --> 36:16.158
I NEED TO TELL YOU SOME THINGS,
WALLACE.

36:17.440 --> 36:20.159
I NEVER LIVED
ON THE UPPER WEST SIDE.

36:20.210 --> 36:22.804
MY MOM ISN'T A MODEL.

36:22.840 --> 36:24.842
SHE'S A WAITRESS...

36:24.880 --> 36:28.816
WHO HAD A ONE-NIGHT STAND
WITH TERRENCE 18 YEARS AGO.

36:29.650 --> 36:31.584
I'M JUST ANOTHER KID
FROM BROOKLYN

36:31.620 --> 36:33.781
WHO GOT SCREWED UP
ON DRUGS AND BOOZE

36:33.820 --> 36:34.855
AND ALL THE WRONG FRIENDS.

36:34.890 --> 36:36.687
BY THE TIME I WAS
A SOPHOMORE --

36:36.720 --> 36:38.779
YOUR PAST REALLY
DOESN'T MATTER TO ME.

36:38.830 --> 36:41.549
I HAVE A SON, WALLACE.

36:41.600 --> 36:43.750
HE'S 2.

36:43.800 --> 36:44.892
WHEN HE WAS BORN,

36:44.930 --> 36:46.818
MY MOM CONTACTED MY DAD
AND MADE A DEAL.

36:46.870 --> 36:49.191
I'D GO TO CALIFORNIA
AND TRY TO START OVER,

36:49.240 --> 36:50.764
AND SHE'D RAISE MY BABY.

36:50.800 --> 36:52.859
WHEN MY DAD JUST DROPPED ME
FROM HIS LIFE,

36:52.910 --> 36:55.879
I REALIZED THAT I WAS
BEING A HYPOCRITE.

36:55.910 --> 36:57.207
HERE I WAS, TORN UP

36:57.240 --> 37:00.448
THAT I WASN'T THE CENTER
OF MY DAD'S UNIVERSE

37:00.480 --> 37:04.211
WHEN MY MOM WAS RAISING MY KID
3,000 MILES AWAY.

37:04.250 --> 37:07.413
I CAN'T BE THAT PERSON,
WALLACE.

37:07.450 --> 37:09.350
I HAD TO COME BACK.

37:12.290 --> 37:15.327
AND I HAVE TO STAY.

37:17.660 --> 37:22.029
AND YOUR LIFE
IS IN NEPTUNE,

37:22.070 --> 37:24.504
AND YOU HAVE TO GO.

37:36.520 --> 37:37.976
[ Normal voice ]
HE MEANS STINKY.

37:38.020 --> 37:40.341
[ Deep voice ] BOTH STINKY.
YOU'RE STINKY!

37:40.390 --> 37:41.652
HONK! HONK!

37:41.690 --> 37:44.284
[ Normal voice ]
HONEY, DO YOU SMELL THAT?

37:44.330 --> 37:45.922
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT IS?

37:45.960 --> 37:48.849
I SMELL BACON.

37:48.900 --> 37:51.562
DAD?

37:59.510 --> 38:01.034
HEY, I'M SORRY.

38:01.070 --> 38:04.005
I'M SORRY.

38:04.040 --> 38:07.271
I'M SO SORRY.

38:07.310 --> 38:09.915
Keith: WAS THAT BREAKFAST
I SMELL?

38:09.950 --> 38:11.781
[ GASPS ] YOU'RE ALIVE!

38:11.820 --> 38:14.914
OH, I THOUGHT
YOU WERE DEAD!

38:14.960 --> 38:16.257
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

38:16.290 --> 38:19.054
OH, HONEY, WHAT'S WRONG?
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

38:19.090 --> 38:23.891
WOODY'S PLANE --
CASSIDY CASABLANCAS BLEW IT UP.

38:23.930 --> 38:26.125
OH, HONEY..

38:26.170 --> 38:27.797
I WASN'T ON THE PLANE.

38:27.830 --> 38:29.263
LAMB DIDN'T WANT ME
ARRIVING

38:29.300 --> 38:30.938
WITH WOODY GETTING MET
BY THE PRESS,

38:30.970 --> 38:33.268
SO HE HAD THEM TAKE ME OFF
THE PLANE AT THE LAST MINUTE.

38:33.310 --> 38:36.768
I RAN TO THE CAR.
I DROVE HOME.

38:36.810 --> 38:38.801
I WAS A LITTLE SURPRISED
TO FIND,

38:38.850 --> 38:40.602
YOU KNOW,
LOGAN ON THE COUCH,

38:40.650 --> 38:43.847
BUT IT WAS BETTER THAN FINDING
HIM ELSEWHERE, RIGHT?

38:43.880 --> 38:45.586
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:47.120 --> 38:50.556
WHAT WERE YOU SAYING
ABOUT THE CASABLANCAS BOY?

38:52.730 --> 38:55.551
IT'S MOST LIKELY GOING TO BE
RULED A SUICIDE,

38:55.600 --> 38:58.524
SO INSURANCE-WISE,
THAT'S GOING TO BE A WASH.

38:58.570 --> 39:03.064
THE COPS FOUND THESE
IN CASSIDY'S ROOM, HOWEVER.

39:03.100 --> 39:06.160
PHOENIX LAND TRUST.
IT'S ALL IN YOUR NAME.

39:06.210 --> 39:08.132
I ASSUME THE --
RIGHT.

39:08.170 --> 39:09.603
PHOENIX,
THE REAL-ESTATE THING.

39:09.640 --> 39:10.902
HOW AM I DOING THESE DAYS?

39:10.940 --> 39:12.168
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:12.210 --> 39:14.303
$8 MILLION AND CHANGE.

39:14.350 --> 39:16.113
TELL HIM I SAID,
"NICE GOING."

39:16.150 --> 39:17.845
HIM?

39:17.880 --> 39:21.088
BETTING AGAINST INCORPORATION?
BALLSY.

39:21.120 --> 39:24.624
FEELS LIKE A RICHARD CASABLANCAS
MOVE TO ME.

39:25.760 --> 39:27.978
I CAN FEEL IT ALREADY.

39:28.030 --> 39:30.897
THE LITTLE-TOWN BLUES
ARE MELTING AWAY.

39:30.930 --> 39:32.466
YOU ALL PACKED?

39:32.500 --> 39:34.092
VAGABOND SHOES AND ALL.

39:34.130 --> 39:35.438
AND PEPPER SPRAY --

39:35.470 --> 39:38.166
FOR IF WE RUN INTO
THAT TRUMP CHARACTER.

39:38.200 --> 39:40.236
YOU SURE YOU DON'T WANT TO DRIVE
WITH THE OLD MAN?

39:40.270 --> 39:43.034
LOGAN IS GIVING ME A RIDE.
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO "TALK."

39:43.080 --> 39:46.140
HOW'D HE TAKE,
UM, WHAT HAPPENED?

39:46.180 --> 39:49.308
SHRUGS IT OFF, CALLS HIMSELF
LITTLE ORPHAN ANNIE,

39:49.350 --> 39:52.683
WHICH I THINK MEANS
"BADLY."

39:54.460 --> 39:55.586
I SHOULD GO OUT FRONT.

39:55.620 --> 39:57.178
I SHOULD GET
MY AUTOGRAPH BOOK.

39:57.220 --> 40:00.587
CAROL CHANNING IS STILL ALIVE,
ISN'T SHE?

40:00.630 --> 40:02.825
I'LL SEE YOU AT THE GATE.

40:07.070 --> 40:09.197
SO?

40:09.240 --> 40:12.698
[ PAUL WESTERBERG'S
"TIME FLIES TOMORROW" PLAYS ]

40:20.010 --> 40:21.477
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

40:21.520 --> 40:23.613
I WON'T SEE YOU
FOR A WHOLE WEEK.

40:23.650 --> 40:25.140
THAT'S, LIKE, FOREVER.

40:25.190 --> 40:28.341
YEAH, BUT THEN I'LL BE BACK,
AND EVERYTHING WILL BE FINE.

40:28.390 --> 40:31.359
* SWING FROM THE CEILING

40:31.390 --> 40:33.722
YOU SAY THAT,
BUT I DON'T KNOW.

40:33.760 --> 40:35.899
I KNOW.
I CAN FEEL IT.

40:35.930 --> 40:38.467
AND YOU'RE NEVER WRONG?
NO?

40:38.500 --> 40:40.627
AW...YOUNG LOVE.

40:40.670 --> 40:42.695
NO, NO, HOLD THAT POSITION.

40:42.740 --> 40:46.232
NORMAN ROCKWELL WANTS TO COME IN
AND PAINT YOU TWO.

40:46.270 --> 40:50.229
DID HE PIN ON HIS PIN,
OR WAS HE TOO SHY?

40:50.280 --> 40:51.599
WHY ARE YOU HERE?

40:51.650 --> 40:52.776
YEAH, I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU COULD COME OUT

40:52.810 --> 40:54.209
DURING DAYLIGHT HOURS.

40:54.250 --> 40:57.344
I HAVE A BUSINESS PROPOSITION
FOR YOUR FATHER.

40:57.380 --> 40:59.245
OKAY,
BUT I'M WARNING YOU.

40:59.290 --> 41:01.144
HE DOESN'T
CARRY MUCH CASH.

41:01.190 --> 41:02.452
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

41:02.490 --> 41:04.310
I NEED YOU TO DO SOMETHING
FOR ME.

41:04.360 --> 41:07.488
WELL, I'LL BE BACK IN A WEEK,
AND AT THAT TIME, I WILL --

41:07.530 --> 41:08.622
I NEED IT RIGHT NOW.

41:08.660 --> 41:09.957
SORRY, MRS. CASABLANCAS,

41:10.000 --> 41:12.321
BUT I'M MEETING MY DAUGHTER
IN AN HOUR.

41:12.370 --> 41:15.589
I THINK
YOU'LL CHANGE YOUR MIND.

41:17.870 --> 41:18.837
OH.

41:18.870 --> 41:22.670
LIKE I SAID,
IT'S IMPORTANT.

41:23.840 --> 41:29.642
* TI-I-I-IME

41:29.680 --> 41:33.241
* FLIES TOMORROW

41:36.790 --> 41:43.753
* AND TOMORROW WILL MAKE A DAY

41:43.800 --> 41:46.860
* SINCE WE'VE MET
